channel.title: Otways Bioscan – Lepidoptera
channel.description:
This lepidoptera survey is conducted by Museums Victoria and Parks Victoria in conjunction with Moths of Victoria team members. **Observations added to this group are restricted to those made during the survey events.
Components of the Bioscan project: • Make comparisons between recently burnt areas with unburnt areas • Prepare a booklet
NOTE: Your information is valuable to the creation of a comprehensive list of species occurring in the Otways. Please join the NatureShare group 'Otway Ranges – Moths'

item.title: Atheropla decaspila
item.dc:creator: petermoth
